  paragraphs:
  - 'AURORA: Careful Cosmo, I sense a large energy signal rapidly approaching your
    location. '
  - "COSMO: Don\u2019t worry Aurora; I see it."
  - "???: Rahahahaha! You there, are you this \u201CCosmo\u201D fellow I\u2019ve
    been hearing all about from my troops? "
  - 'COSMO: Maybe I am, maybe I am not. State your business. '
  - "???: General Glorgus. The number one general in charge of \u2018Specimen X\u2019."
  - "COSMO: So, you\u2019re the fiend behind this attack. Then yes, I am Cosmo. And
    I am here to dismantle your entire fleet and stop your attacks on our planet
    for good. "
  - "GENERAL GLORGUS: I\u2019m not one for chit chat especially with the enemy. Let
    us fight! "
  - "AURORA: Watch out Cosmo, if he\u2019s their General, he must be strong. "
  - "COSMO: I\u2019ll handle it Aurora, especially with you by my side."
  - "GENERAL GLORGUS: Are we fighting or are we talking? I\u2019m waiting."
  - "AURORA: Let\u2019s get him then."
  - 'COSMO: Let''s'
